text: Khetag Gozyumov (born 24 April 1981 in Alagir, North Ossetian ASSR) is an Azerbaijani wrestler of Ossetian origin. He won a bronze medal at the 2008 Summer Olympics and 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Azerbaijani wrestlers Category:Olympic bronze medalists Category:Olympians for Azerbaijan Category:Olympic silver medalists Category:Medalists at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Medalists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:21st- century Azerbaijani people
